{"tid":323593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家打work，用開咩字體？？","createTime":"2017-07-15T17:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T19:39:26.000Z","uid":105534,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd8ce0c7cf8e861dbf47949d2b74603126b3bc4","tid":323593,"uid":105534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早排幫老豆打啲文件野比人<br />\n發現新細明體好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下巴絲們平時用開邊種字體？！<br />\n中英文都講得<br />\n<br />\n利申：中文用 自由香港楷書；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n            英文無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6688537596215755d47f815d2c18540b96577f","tid":323593,"uid":14004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"打work?"},{"pid":"a73f7889f91838c59f23b6c502c305c012f58fe5","tid":323593,"uid":128595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:20:10.000Z","msg":"如果係FOR客,<br />\n都係大路果d黑體 &amp; helvetica,<br />\n用D冷門字型,<br />\n個客部腦無既話仲核突,<br />\n又怕移位<br />\n<br />\nprint out 另計"},{"pid":"9137d5de37bc48fff32d1fbd8beb8e295ec6d62a","tid":323593,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"但係明體反而先最清晰易讀<br />\n<br />\n黑體睇落靚仔，但唔一定適合閱讀（而且有啲設計嘅人好抗拒，啲人濫用，特別係微軟正黑體）<br />\n<br />\nGoogle＋Adobe出嘅思源黑體唔錯，仲有Apple出嘅蘋方都係<br />\n<br />\n但畀我㨂睇一本書，一定想睇明體多過黑體，舒服好多<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n答返樓主問題<br />\n其實你用微軟正黑體咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784dea56f2b556d4179c9fe8b5d48f06ba6c874f","tid":323593,"uid":27188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"睇文件見到新細明體會個人好炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有道氣頂住頂住<br />\n一定要改哂做Calibri先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dddf509cd